&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and research target accounts, aligning prospects to the most relevant CB Insights use cases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute high-volume, multi-channel outreach (phone, email, LinkedIn) to meet weekly KPIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Qualify inbound leads from marketing campaigns, content engagement, and demo requests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Schedule introductory platform calls that convert into qualified sales opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Account Executives and Customer Success to support opportunity progression and close&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate and up-to-date prospecting activity in the CRM to ensure data integrity and reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Sales and Marketing to refine messaging, targeting, and outreach strategies based on market and prospect insights&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistently meet or exceed monthly and quarterly opportunity and demo targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in ongoing training to deepen product, industry, and sales expertise&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Share prospect feedback to inform product positioning, messaging, and go-to-market strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you bring to the table:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BA/BS degree (or relevant work experience)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years of SDR, sales or relevant experience with a history of overachieving targets around new business acquisition or customer engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication skills over both phone and email&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creative problem-solving abilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Desire to move up within a sales organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
